'''鸻形目'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|Charadriiformes}}）在[[生物分类学|生物分类学]]上是[[鸟纲|鸟纲]]中的一个[[目_(生物)|目]]，包括[[鸻科|鸻]]、[[鷸科|鷸]]、[[鷗科|鷗]]等，大多屬小型[[涉禽|涉禽]]。分子生物學家通過{{link-en|DNA雜交實驗|DNA–DNA hybridization}}發現，本目跟[[火烈鳥目|紅鶴目]]的DNA較接近。在2015年的研究中認為與[[奇蹟鳥類|奇蹟鳥類]]（Mirandornithes）親緣相近。<ref name="Prum2015">{{Cite journal|title=A comprehensive phylogeny of birds (Aves) using targeted next-generation DNA sequencing|url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v526/n7574/full/nature15697.html|last=Prum|first=R. O.|date=22 October 2015|journal=Nature|issue=7574|doi=10.1038/nature15697|volume=526|pages=569–573|pmid=26444237|display-authors=etal|access-date=2019-11-23|archive-date=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529060101/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v526/n7574/full/nature15697.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但在2020年的另一份研究中則認為與[[鶴形目|鶴形目]]（Gruiformes）親緣相近。<ref name=Kuhletal2020>{{cite journal | first1 = H. | last1 = Kuhl | first2 = C. | last2 = Frankl-Vilches | first3 = A. | last3 = Bakker | first4 = G. | last4 = Mayr | first5 = G. | last5 = Nikolaus | first6 = S. T. | last6 = Boerno | first7 = S. | last7 = Klages | first8 = B. | last8 = Timmermann | first9 = M. | last9 = Gahr | year = 2020 | title = An unbiased molecular approach using 3’UTRs resolves the avian family-level tree of life. | journal = Molecular Biology and Evolution | pages = 143 | doi = 10.1093/molbev/msaa191|pmc=7783168  | doi-access = free }}</ref>

